meanings: (탈것에) ride, take; (올라타다) get on, get in(to), board
(흐름·틈 등을) take advantage of, capitalize on
(불에) burn, blaze; (화염에 휩싸이다) be in flames (=불타다)
tan, (피부가) be suntanned, be browned; (지나치게) be sunburned
(액체·가루 등을 섞다) mix (up), add; (물로 희석하다) dilute, water down
